name_as_recorded: Bequeathed to Conception Abbey by Dr. Charles D. Humberd of Barnard, Missouri.
Brought from the library of Engelberg Abbey in Switzerland to Conception Abbey sometime before 1900.
Came to Conception Abbey from its motherhouse, Engelberg in Switzerland.
Price in English pounds on the recto, suggesting that the leaf may have been a gift to Conception Abbey from Dr. Charles D. Humberd (1876-1966) of Bernard, Missouri (buried in West Union, Indiana).
